headline: Interactive Brokers Hits Buy Point As This Key Event Looms
summary: Interactive Brokers is the IBD Stock of the Day as shares trade near a buy point after Tuesday's breakout.  The online brokerage firm's profit growth has slowed over the past several quarters.  Interactive Brokers averaged earnings-per-share gains of 21.4% in the past three quarters, according to IBD Stock Checkup.
